Played all my life music of and in the style of the H.C.Q of France.  Actve in Quebec since 1998.  I have three records: on Carrere label ( france ) quintet with Raphael Fays top gypsy guitarist Django style. on J.A.C. label ( canada ) quartet with Serge Krief great french guitarist and J.A.C. label ( canada ) quintet also with Serge Krief.
